{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n180\u2089 = 1\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 1\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 0\u00d71 = 81 + 72 + 0 = 153\u2081\u2080\n\n345\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 243 + 36 + 5 = 284\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n153 \u00d7 284 = 153 \u00d7 (300 - 16) = 45,900 - 2,448 = 43,452\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n43452 \u00f7 9 = 4828 r 0\n4828 \u00f7 9 = 536 r 4\n536 \u00f7 9 = 59 r 5\n59 \u00f7 9 = 6 r 5\n6 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 6\n\nReading from bottom to top: 65540\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n65540\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u2074 + 5\u00d79\u00b3 + 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d76561 + 5\u00d7729 + 5\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 0 = 39366 + 3645 + 405 + 36 + 0 = 43,452\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n**65540**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 461}